  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eSome of Canada’s most darling design vernacular is recorded within the historic walls of urban dwellings that continue to endear audiences. Architect\u003cstrong\u003e Biran O’Brian\u003c/strong\u003e of \u003ca href=\"https://www.worksoffice.com/works\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWORKS OFFICE\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, in collaboration with interior designer \u003ca href=\"https://gilliansegaldesign.com/portfolio/ghouse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGillian Segal\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, adds to the country’s rich architectural accomplishments with a charming residential renovation project in Vancouver’s enviable Annex neighborhood. Here, a distinct heritage is infused with modern ingenuity for a Victorian-era informed domicile contemporized through Art Deco detailing. Bold geometry, striking forms, and inky hues all help to bridge the gap between past and present visual languages while leaving room for dialogue into the future.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558793\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558793\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-28-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Modern, multi-story brick building with a combination of traditional red bricks and unique copper cladding featuring a circular window and contemporary design elements.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-28-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-28-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/im