der aspects of any space.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558770\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558770\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-05-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern living room features a round skylight, striped sofa, two red armchairs, glass coffee table, metal chairs, floor lamp with a woven shade, and wall art. Background has dining area with hanging light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-05-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-05-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-05-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-05.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558771\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558771\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-06-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Image of a modern, semi-circular rooftop window with sunlight streaming through, showcasing a geometric ceiling design with overlapping wooden and metal elements.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-06-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-06-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-06-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-06.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe 3,900-square-foot residence is only typical of modern new-builds as it unfurls programmatically: a sprawling open kitchen, dining, and living space on the ground floor; bedrooms and a study on the first floor; guest and principal suites on the second floor; and a lower level housing the lounge and gym. Spatial and aesthetic solutions, as teased by the exterior, are delightfully nuanced.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558772\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558772\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-07-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with a large marble island, three stools, a brass faucet, and red cabinetry. Beige tiles cover the backsplash, and a contemporary ceiling light fixture is visible.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-07-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-07-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-07-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-07-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-07.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558773\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558773\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-08-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A kitchen with terra-cotta cabinets, a black oven with multiple knobs, a tiled backsplash, and a countertop with a vase holding a large flower. Cooking utensils are placed in a cup next to the oven.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-08-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-08-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-08-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-08-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-08.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe clients, a family of four, invite excitement and intrigue inside with treatments carefully curated by Segal to create interest from tension between existing elements and contemporary concepts. Stained wainscoting and cement tile applied in a classic checkerboard pattern reference historical traditions whereas unexpected textures, extruded walls, and unique approaches to daylighting appeal to contemporary sensibilities. Daring reds, dark greens, and deep blues exude grandeur from cabinets, countertops, carpets, and upholstery in primarily public areas contrasted by more private spaces awash in dreamier hues or creamy off-whites.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558774\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558774\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-09-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen and living area with light wood flooring, red cabinetry, curved white staircase, open shelving, and mesh chairs. Decor includes a wall-mounted plate and a magazine on the coffee table.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-09-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-09-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-09-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-09.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558775\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558775\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-10-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A person walks up a staircase in a modern white-walled building with curved architectural elements and a skylight.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-10-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-10-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-10-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-10-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSubversive home furnishings also heighten the awareness of duality as it exists in the home. Though dubious looking, the silver ‘chainmail’ chairs are surprisingly comfortable. And lighting fixtures by Anna Karlin and Josef Hoffman nod to the Art Deco era without being ostentatious resulting in approachable sculptural forms.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558776\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558776\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-11-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A staircase is shown from below, with curving white walls and a round window at the top letting in light. A line of spherical lights is mounted on the right wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-11-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-11-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=558777\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-558777\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-12-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A modern white staircase with wooden handrails, featuring a large abstract painting and a round ceiling light overhead.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-12-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-12-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-12-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-12-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/Gillian-Segal-Design-The-Anex-House-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“This project was a very paired down, modern interpretation – things were focused. Streamlined forms. Rich, bold, and unique materiality. While something truly authentic to Art Deco would be overwhelming in today’s world,” Segal explains. “Using select components and reinterpreting for this project created something that feels very warm, bold, special, and timeless.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\